了，而这也是他对得起老祖宗的方式。 晚年虽患病，但郭宝昌仍笔耕不辍，80 岁提笔，83 岁含血带泪的 60 万字长篇小说《大宅门》定稿，他说，「每到大风起兮的时候，我的思绪总随着风回到那个年代…」如今，心愿达成的郭宝昌随宅门风云而去，这一辈子做了太多事，又好像只做了一件事，那就是《大宅门》。 文 / 北京青年报记者 郭佳导演郭宝昌去世，离世前刚刚完成长篇小说《大宅门》_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-35edb1479ce765307f6999ee3f0d0245_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625785565"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwOWEqeOFnp5mEAMaCTEwMTM0MjQ2NCDWyp6pBjAAOLkCQClyCTYyNTc4NTU2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1697436501.795301", "card_id": "Q_543705116", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 553}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "每天坚持晨跑 5 公里，会怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-984732bdcda2a96c1f99f7d008fd9035_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/543705116"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwOWEqeOFnp5mEAMaCDgzMTA1OTAwIPDfy5YGMAA4qA5AKnIJNTQzNzA1MTE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1697436501.795678", "card_id": "Q_622481932", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 289}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "最近刚换了 4070ti，但是游戏掉帧更严重了。请问我这套配置哪里出了问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近在玩的堡垒之夜和博得之门 3 尤为严，LoL 帧率浮动也很大，60 到 130 之间，永杰无间也算不上流程，会有卡顿情况发生。死亡搁浅反而相对流程很多。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-84bcf250b0fa816cd9a6309c70e70239_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/622481932"}}, "attached_info"